headline: Pop-Tarts® Dials Up the Crazy Good Drama as Three Edible Mascots Compete to be Eaten at the 2024 Pop-Tarts Bowl
summary: How does Pop-Tarts® top the first-ever Edible Mascot, an overnight internet sensation? They triple it! The Pop-Tarts Bowl is back with three times the Crazy Goodness as the highly anticipated game won't just play out between two college football teams – it'll be happening between three Pop-Tarts Edible Mascots, too. All for the ultimate pastry glory of being the game-winning snack for the Pop-Tarts Bowl victors.
